title: PCSX2_Portable_64MBMemoryCards.7z
description:
Hi PS2 games friends ...


... and this file have the latest stable version of the PCSX2 emulator with complete portability (all the folders and files are packed in a sigle executable) with only a single folder outside of the pcsx2 executable with 2 memory cards with 64 mega each for your PS2 saves and with an appropriate memory cards managers to help circulating and converting saves anytime the user want ...



Gaming Is For Everyone ...


and happy PS2 games to all of you ...
